a man in the window.

194
00:13:16,428 --> 00:13:17,918
I couldn't find him.

195
00:13:19,198 --> 00:13:20,460
Where?

196
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,933
Show me.

197
00:13:26,238 --> 00:13:27,865
He was right there.

198
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,100
What did he
look like, baby?

199
00:13:29,175 --> 00:13:30,767
TRISH: She said
he had a big head.

200
00:13:30,843 --> 00:13:32,242
And it was fuzzy.

201
00:13:33,145 --> 00:13:35,409
LIBBY: (CHUCKLES) Fuzzy?

202
00:13:35,748 --> 00:13:37,010
