558
00:39:09,246 --> 00:39:10,713
(ENGINE REVVING)

559
00:39:10,781 --> 00:39:12,373
Just stay here.

560
00:39:12,817 --> 00:39:13,943
(REVVING)

561
00:39:19,123 --> 00:39:22,286
What are you doing?
What the hell are you doing?

562
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:25,888
