(SCREAMING)

624
00:42:55,039 --> 00:42:56,097
(TAPS ON KEYBOARD)

625
00:42:56,173 --> 00:42:57,538
WILL: That's Ann Patterson.

626
00:42:57,808 --> 00:43:00,902
She's... She lives
across the road from us.

627
00:43:01,712 --> 00:43:03,646
I knew she knew him.

628
00:43:05,516 --> 00:43:08,110
Let's go on.
You'll understand.

629
00:43:10,988 --> 00:43:12,455
At a certain point,

630
00:43:12,523 --> 00:43:14,923
