633
00:43:19,196 --> 00:43:21,061
Well, what's
he doing now?

634
00:43:21,131 --> 00:43:24,999
He refused to allow his name to
appear on any of the hospital IDs.

635
00:43:25,069 --> 00:43:27,537
So he chewed them off

636
00:43:28,872 --> 00:43:30,897
