651
00:44:47,384 --> 00:44:49,750
The numbers 8-10-10

652
00:44:50,287 --> 00:44:51,982
become Atenton.

653
00:44:52,823 --> 00:44:55,519
Will Atenton.

654
00:45:00,464 --> 00:45:02,898
I don't believe
any of this.

655
00:45:02,966 --> 00:45:05,161
You're a danger
to yourself.

656
00:45:06,136 --> 00:45:07,797
And to others.

657
00:45:09,306 --> 00:45:13,072
I'm sure the scar where your wife shot you is still there.

658
00:45:15,245 --> 00:45:16,837
That would...

659
00:45:20,684 --> 00:45:22,743
That would mean that...

660
00:45:38,035 --> 00:45:39,366
(SOBBING)

661
00:45:56,854 --> 00:45:58,014
No.

662
00:46:02,860 --> 00:46:06,193
I left my wife and my family at home this morning.

663
00:46:07,531 --> 00:46:10,125
You murdered your
wife and family

664
00:46:10,868 --> 00:46:12,529
five years ago.

665
00:46:14,338 --> 00:46:15,498
(STAMMERS)

666
00:46:21,044 --> 00:46:23,069
You're a fucking liar!

667
00:46:24,548 --> 00:46:25,810
All right, move in.

668
00:46:26,483 --> 00:46:27,711
