692
00:47:53,270 --> 00:47:56,467
(SOBBING)
Will... Will...

693
00:47:56,907 --> 00:47:58,272
(SPEAKS MANDARIN)

694
00:47:59,443 --> 00:48:00,501
(DOOR BUZZES)

695
00:48:56,033 --> 00:48:57,364
(CREAKING)

696
00:49:24,528 --> 00:49:25,859
(CREAKING)

697
00:49:52,022 --> 00:49:53,785
(BREATHING RAPIDLY)

698
00:49:55,459 --> 00:49:56,892
(SCREAMS)

699
00:50:30,327 --> 00:50:31,521
(GRUNTS)

700
00:51:06,897 --> 00:51:08,990
LIBBY: Thanks for the flowers.

701
00:51:21,678 --> 00:51:23,270
