728
00:52:55,605 --> 00:52:56,663
All right?

729
00:52:56,740 --> 00:52:59,834
I'm just gonna talk to
Daddy for a little bit.

730
00:53:00,243 --> 00:53:01,301
Stay there!

731
00:53:03,513 --> 00:53:06,073
