01:15:14,042 --> 01:15:15,202
(GASPING)

1050
01:15:16,478 --> 01:15:17,911
Peter!

1051
01:15:19,348 --> 01:15:21,213
ANN: Jack, you killed them.

1052
01:15:21,383 --> 01:15:22,577
JACK: It was supposed
to be you.

1053
01:15:22,651 --> 01:15:23,743
(FISTS POUNDING)

1054
01:15:23,819 --> 01:15:24,945
Stop!

1055
01:15:27,689 --> 01:15:28,917
(GRUNTING)

1056
01:15:30,392 --> 01:15:32,587
Get the chloroform! Now!

1057
01:15:36,164 --> 01:15:37,563
(CHOKING)

1058
01:15:54,583 --> 01:15:56,915
JACK: It should've
been so simple.

1059
01:15:57,519 --> 01:16:00,488
BOYCE: I went to the wrong goddamn house.
It was a mistake.

1060
01:16:00,556 --> 01:16:02,524
JACK: We put them
in the basement.

1061
01:16:10,232 --> 01:16:11,358
(OPENS DOOR)

1062
01:16:11,433 --> 01:16:12,525
(BELLS TINKLING)

1063
01:16:21,476 --> 01:16:23,000
Where are you?

1064
01:16:23,078 --> 01:16:24,739
BOYCE ON PHONE:
I'm pulling up right now.

1065
01:16:25,681 --> 01:16:28,878
First right on Bramble Branch,
third house on the right.

1066
01:16:29,051 --> 01:16:32,077
I'm outside the house.
I'm looking at Jack's wife right now.

1067
01:16:33,889 --> 01:16:35,083
Where is she?

1068
01:16:35,157 --> 01:16:36,852
She's talking to
someone on her cell.

1069
01:16:38,327 --> 01:16:39,794
Who's she talking to?

1070
01:16:39,861 --> 01:16:41,260
I don't know.

1071
01:16:41,330 --> 01:16:44,197
Maybe that young boyfriend
you were talking about.

1072
01:16:45,467 --> 01:16:47,901
JACK ON PHONE:
You got the gun I gave you last night?

1073
01:16:47,970 --> 01:16:48,994
BOYCE ON PHONE: Yeah.

1074
01:16:49,137 --> 01:16:50,661
Well, use it.

1075
01:16:51,473 --> 01:16:54,067
And then just drift on out of New Ashford like I told you.

1076
01:16:54,142 --> 01:16:55,507
The insurance money
is real, right?

1077
01:16:55,577 --> 01:16:56,669
You'll get paid.

1078
01:16:56,945 --> 01:17:00,381
I know we don't know each other that well,
but after tonight

1079
01:17:00,949 --> 01:17:04,680
you got something on me,
I got something on you.

1080
01:17:04,886 --> 01:17:06,911
We gotta trust
each other.

1081
01:17:06,989 --> 01:17:08,957
You sure you want
me to do this?

1082
01:17:09,091 --> 01:17:11,889
What right has she got
to destroy my life?

1083
01:17:12,527 --> 01:17:14,518
What right has she
got to my daughter?

1084
01:17:14,596 --> 01:17:16,791
Your call. Last chance
to back out of this.

1085
01:17:20,602 --> 01:17:21,762
Kill her now.

1086
01:17:27,376 --> 01:17:28,536
(GRUNTS)

1087
01:17:41,823 --> 01:17:42,915
(GUN FIRES)
(GRUNTS)

1088
01:17:43,625 --> 01:17:45,092
I'm sick of
your shit.

1089
01:17:45,260 --> 01:17:47,785
You've tormented me
for five goddamn years.

1090
01:17:48,063 --> 01:17:49,394
Child killer.

1091
01:17:49,464 --> 01:17:50,522
(GUN FIRES)

1092
01:17:50,899 --> 01:17:52,093
(GROANS)

1093
01:18:05,580 --> 01:18:06,569
Come on.

1094
01:18:08,417 --> 01:18:09,975
You'll never collect.

1095
01:18:10,686 --> 01:18:12,984
Chloe collects,
I collect.

1096
01:18:15,457 --> 01:18:16,754
(BELLS TINKLING)

1097
01:18:18,860 --> 01:18:20,327
(DOOR CREAKING)

1098
01:18:44,319 --> 01:18:47,948
You took everything.
My money, my house, my kid!

1099
01:18:49,224 --> 01:18:51,249
And now that Ward's back,

1100
01:18:52,728 --> 01:18:54,320
I get another shot.

1101
01:19:05,707 --> 01:19:07,004
(GRUNTING)

1102
01:19:26,628 --> 01:19:27,788
(THUDDING)

1103
01:19:27,863 --> 01:19:29,194
(POURING)

1104
01:19:40,175 --> 01:19:41,335
Peter.

1105
01:19:42,210 --> 01:19:43,734
(GROANING)

1106
01:19:56,057 --> 01:19:57,081
Peter?

1107
01:19:58,994 --> 01:20:02,088
Peter! Wake up, Peter!

1108
01:20:21,082 --> 01:20:22,310
(RUMBLING)

1109
01:20:37,766 --> 01:20:38,926
Okay, Ward!

1110
01:20:39,034 --> 01:20:40,160
(GROANS)

1111
01:20:44,239 --> 01:20:46,935
ANN: Peter. Peter.

1112
01:20:50,478 --> 01:20:52,378
You're all right.
You're all right. You're okay.

1113
01:21:01,756 --> 01:21:02,984
(GUN FIRING)

1114
01:21:14,336 --> 01:21:15,701
(GRUNTING)

1115
01:21:26,081 --> 01:21:27,139
(FIRES)

1116
01:21:29,417 --> 01:21:30,714
(SCREAMING)

1117
01:21:49,170 --> 01:21:50,637
(ANN COUGHING)

1118
01:21:53,541 --> 01:21:54,530
Are you okay?

1119
01:21:55,176 --> 01:21:56,973
Yes.
Chloe!

1120
01:21:57,913 --> 01:22:00,746
CHLOE: Mom! Mom!

1121
01:22:04,352 --> 01:22:05,717
Oh, baby.

1122
01:22:10,592 --> 01:22:12,560
Peter, no!

1123
01:22:19,668 --> 01:22:22,603
Libby! Libby!

1124
01:22:28,410 --> 01:22:29,741
(RUMBLING)

1125
01:22:32,747 --> 01:22:34,874
What are you doing?
Get out of here.

1126
01:22:36,351 --> 01:22:38,080
I don't wanna lose you.

1127
01:22:39,854 --> 01:22:43,881
I know,
but you have to go.

1128
01:23:04,946 --> 01:23:06,243
You be good.

1129
01:23:06,314 --> 01:23:07,838
We love you, Daddy.

1130
01:23:34,709 --> 01:23:36,267
I love you.

1131
01:23:38,313 --> 01:23:40,042
I love you.

1132
01:23:45,186 --> 01:23:46,710
I'll always be with you.

1133
01:23:47,322 --> 01:23:48,789
I know.

1134
01:23:51,793 --> 01:23:53,317
But you know that.

1135
01:23:57,699 --> 01:23:58,859
(GASPS)

1136
01:24:21,923 --> 01:24:23,447
(SIREN WAILING)

1137
01:24:32,634 --> 01:24:33,658
Is there anybody
else inside?

1138
01:24:33,735 --> 01:24:34,963
No.

1139
01:24:35,036 --> 01:24:36,901
You okay?
Yeah.
